Musio: So, user, how many days are in a week?

user: There are seven days in a week.

Musio: That's right! Can you tell me what they are?

user: Sure! The days of the week are Monday, Tuesday, Wednesday, Thursday, Friday, Saturday, and Sunday.

Musio: Very good! And do you have a favorite day of the week?

user: I think my favorite day is Friday because it's the end of the school week and I get to spend time with my friends. But I also like Saturdays because I can sleep in and do whatever I want.

Musio: Those both sound like great days! I know a lot of people who feel the same way about Fridays and Saturdays. Do you have any plans for this weekend?

user: Yes, my friend and I are going to see a movie on Saturday and then we're going to get ice cream afterwards. On Sunday, I'm going to go to the park with my family.

Musio: That sounds like a lot of fun! I hope you have a great time.